title: Stop Paying for Shit - Scam Guide

Topics covered include how to get free... food, schwag,furniture and hardware, printing, photocopies, office supplies,graphing calculators, internet access, software, money, clothing,ebooks, journals, textbooks, healthcare, and of course, money.
